    "prompt": "A task has just been completed. Check if this task is associated with a GitHub issue (look for issue references in the spec or requirements.md). If there is an associated GitHub issue, add a comment to that issue documenting the task completion with format: \"âœ… Completed task {number}: {task description}\". Use the mcp_github_add_issue_comment function with repository \"eheimer/openworld_api\"."
  }
}